Development Tech Sheet — MVP

System: Hyperliquid spot + Polymarket binary/range overlays

1. Scope

Build an MVP that:
	•	reads spot market data and submits spot orders on Hyperliquid,
	•	reads market/orderbook data and optionally submits orders on Polymarket,
	•	evaluates only spot + Polymarket overlay combinations,
	•	never stops on recoverable API failures,
	•	supports paper mode first, then live mode. Hyperliquid exposes public API, info, exchange, WebSocket, and mainnet/testnet endpoints. Polymarket separates public market data from authenticated CLOB trading, with public read endpoints and authenticated order/cancel flows.  ￼

