5. Essential formulas

Use only these in MVP:

Spot leg
	•	spot_qty = spot_notional / entry_spot
	•	spot_pnl = spot_qty * (exit_spot - entry_spot)

Polymarket long binary/range leg
	•	max_loss = stake
	•	max_profit = stake * ((1 / entry_price) - 1)

Combined
	•	combined_pnl = spot_pnl + pm_leg_pnl - fees - slippage

Risk filters
	•	risk_cost_pct = probable_drawdown / deployed_capital
	•	backup_efficiency = unhedged_drawdown - hedged_drawdown
	•	backup_cost_ratio = backup_cost / gross_target_payoff

