11. MVP deliverable

At MVP completion, system must:
	•	connect to both venues,
	•	read spot and market data,
	•	evaluate one valid strategy family,
	•	filter invalid combinations,
	•	run in paper mode without stopping on transient API failures,
	•	be ready for controlled live execution.
